➜朝鲜的移动洲际导弹是假货？
https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=34623	17910
<div align="center"><a href="http://img.solidot.com.cn/0/366/li6tEXUW2s3po.jpg"><img src="http://img.solidot.com.cn/0/366/li6tEXUW2s3po.jpg" align="" height="244" width="420"></a><br>
</div>
<br>
朝鲜是不涩于对美国进行核恐吓的，它已经三番两次声明要消灭美利坚。它手中的最先进导弹是所谓的KN-08（大浦东C号）。<a target="_blank" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/KN-08"><u>KN-08</u></a>被认为是一种架在重型卡车上的移动式洲际导弹，首次展示是在2012年4月庆祝金日成诞辰一百周年的阅兵式上。德国航空工程师 Markus Schiller从公布的视频和静态照片中发现了疑点，阅兵式共展示了六枚KN-08导弹，每一枚都与另一枚存在差异，比如第一枚导弹的第一级比第二枚导弹的第一级长。其他专家也都注意到了这些异常现象。他们还发现燃料喷嘴的位置很奇怪，弹头看上去是用廉价金属片或木头制造的，等等等等。多数专家都相信，<a target="_blank" href="http://www.npr.org/2013/05/07/181961581/are-those-north-korean-long-range-missiles-for-real#"><u>阅兵式上的导弹不是真的</u></a>。
➜研究称猪流感在中国十分普遍
https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=34624	26465
科学家在周三<a target="_blank" href="http://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/1232798/flu-infections-rising-among-pigs-southern-china-says-study"><u>表示</u></a>，中国南方和东南方养猪场猪流感的感染率在上升，因此新型流感传播到人类的风险在增加。<a target="_blank" href="http://rspb.royalsocietypublishing.org/content/280/1750/20122173.abstract?sid=42fcee96-1f38-4213-9ce4-fa49ff950a70"><u>研究报告</u></a>发表在《英国皇家学会学报B》上。猪可以作为不同流感病毒基因重组的混合容器，酝酿出可以在人类和禽类之间传播的新毒株。中国目前正面临<span id="result_box" class="" lang="zh-CN"><span title="China is currently in the grips of a deadly H7N9 bird flu virus that has killed 27 people since March, mainly in the country's east – overlapping with the study area."><a target="_blank" href="http://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/H7N9"><u>H7N9疫情</u></a>，</span></span><span id="result_box" class="" lang="zh-CN"><span title="China is currently in the grips of a deadly H7N9 bird flu virus that has killed 27 people since March, mainly in the country's east – overlapping with the study area.">H7N9病毒的源头还没有跟踪到猪，尚未发现病毒能在人之间传播。</span></span><span id="result_box" class="" lang="zh-CN"><span title="China is currently in the grips of a deadly H7N9 bird flu virus that has killed 27 people since March, mainly in the country's east – overlapping with the study area."></span></span><span id="result_box" class="" lang="zh-CN"><span title="China is currently in the grips of a deadly H7N9 bird flu virus that has killed 27 people since March, mainly in the country's east – overlapping with the study area.">H7N9病毒已造成31人死亡。研究人员指出，中国是世界上最大的猪肉生产和消费国，因此需要养殖大量的猪。研究作者同时强调，他们的发现并不意味着中国饲养的猪的流感感染率高于其它国家。</span></span>
